long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This Chrome extension brings two of the most powerful and prestigious supercars to your new tab. Watch as the Ferrari and Koenigsegg come to life in stunning detail, showcasing their sleek designs and unrivaled performance. Whether you're a car enthusiast or just love luxury sports cars, this wallpaper will bring a touch of speed and elegance to your browser.

Features:
🚗 Ferrari and Koenigsegg live wallpaper that highlights the power and elegance of these supercars.
🌐 Customizable search bar to use your preferred search engine.
🕒 Clock and date display to keep you organized.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts for easy navigation to your favorite websites.
Let the exhilarating presence of these supercars redefine your browsing experience, adding a dash of luxury and speed to each new tab you open.
